2477
01:26:46,720 --> 01:26:49,280
He has something like a newcomer's
exclusive privilege.

2478
01:26:50,440 --> 01:26:51,800
Can he do that?

2479
01:26:51,800 --> 01:26:53,520
That's too cruel.

2480
01:26:53,520 --> 01:26:55,040
Could you drive faster, please?

2481
01:26:55,040 --> 01:26:56,520
- Hurry.
- Hurry.

2482
01:26:58,920 --> 01:26:59,776
Who is it?

2483
01:27:01,184 --> 01:27:02,040
(So cool.)

2484
01:27:02,040 --> 01:27:03,200
(This is kind of handsome.)

2485
01:27:03,400 --> 01:27:04,480
(Come on.)

2486
01:27:04,480 --> 01:27:06,120
(Hurry up.)

2487
01:27:06,120 --> 01:27:08,040
(I think today's new male guest)

2488
01:27:08,040 --> 01:27:09,320
(poses no threat.)

2489
01:27:09,320 --> 01:27:11,400
The boss has arrived.

2490
01:27:11,400 --> 01:27:12,960
Oh, my God!

2491
01:27:12,960 --> 01:27:14,520
The boss starts.

2492
01:27:14,520 --> 01:27:17,000
The boss has already gone
into full attack mode.

2493
01:27:17,520 --> 01:27:19,400
Guys' exclusive secret tasks.

2494
01:27:19,400 --> 01:27:20,480
(Guys' exclusive invitation task)
Randomly draw

2495
01:27:20,480 --> 01:27:21,520
(Blind box task)
a blind-box task card.

2496
01:27:21,520 --> 01:27:23,200
Complete the task
and successfully invite her.

2497
01:27:26,120 --> 01:27:28,480
I was just kidding.

2498
01:27:28,512 --> 01:27:30,880
(Can the guys complete the secret tasks
and meet someone they fancy?)

2499
01:27:30,880 --> 01:27:32,520
You danced really well.
You didn't make any mistakes earlier.

2500
01:27:32,520 --> 01:27:33,408
One, two, three.

2501
01:27:35,520 --> 01:27:36,720
One, two, three.

2502
01:27:37,400 --> 01:27:38,800
- You made this?
- Yes.

2503
01:27:39,640 --> 01:27:40,704
Smells great.

2504
01:27:40,928 --> 01:27:42,016
Amazing.

2505
01:27:46,840 --> 01:27:49,800
Share the top three impressions
after moving into the house.

2506
01:27:56,000 --> 01:27:57,320
This question seems

2507
01:27:57,880 --> 01:27:58,960
to be an exciting one.

2508
01:27:59,720 --> 01:28:00,960
What perfume is she wearing?

2509
01:28:01,080 --> 01:28:02,160
I'm not familiar with perfumes, but...

2510
01:28:02,160 --> 01:28:02,874
(Secret)

2511
01:28:03,120 --> 01:28:04,000
So who did you look at?

2512
01:28:04,720 --> 01:28:06,440
They're so naughty, all of them.

2513
01:28:06,600 --> 01:28:07,680
I'm terrible at games.

2514
01:28:08,720 --> 01:28:09,560
Me too.

2515
01:28:09,560 --> 01:28:10,520
I have a child.

2516
01:28:10,520 --> 01:28:11,480
I also have a child.

2517
01:28:15,080 --> 01:28:16,600
It's not just sparks. It's fireworks.

2518
01:28:16,600 --> 01:28:18,080
Pink bubbles are overflowing the screen.

2519
01:28:18,200 --> 01:28:19,960
That's so straightforward.

2520
01:28:22,920 --> 01:28:24,080
Don't do it like this.

2521
01:28:26,600 --> 01:28:27,760
(Help me)
Should I start covering my mouth?

2522
01:29:07,678 --> 01:29:24,928
(Love Actually S5 tracking calendar)
